trans-unit.source: Demo files for the Data import/export framework
Demo files for the Data import/export framework
The demo files can be used together with the Contoso demo data for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012.
Specifically, the files are intended to be used together with the CEU Contoso Entertainment Systems (West) company.
Source data format settings for demo files
The following table lists the configuration settings that you should enter for the source data format.
The following table lists the demo files that are associated with each entity.
